<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="fr">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8" />
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
<meta name="color-scheme" content="light dark" />
<meta name="theme-color" content="#0a0a0a" />
<title>ROYAL POP — Swatch × Audemars Piguet</title>
<meta name="description" content="La collection Royal Pop, fruit de la collaboration Swatch × Audemars Piguet. Montres de poche en Bioceramic, livraison 24/72h partout en France." />
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com">
<link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin>
<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Fraunces:opsz,wght@9..144,300;9..144,400;9..144,500;9..144,600;9..144,700;9..144,900&family=Geist+Mono:wght@300;400;500;600&family=Inter+Tight:wght@300;400;500;600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
<style>
  :root{
    --bg-dark:#0a0a0a;
    --bg-dark-2:#111111;
    --bg-light:#f0e9da;
    --bg-light-2:#e8e0cc;
    --ink-on-dark:#f4f1ea;
    --ink-dim-on-dark:#a8a397;
    --ink-on-light:#0a0a0a;
    --ink-dim-on-light:#5a5448;
    --gold-on-dark:#e8c98a;
    --gold-on-light:#a07d2c;
    --line-dark:#1f1f1f;
    --line-light:#d6cdb3;
    --serif:'Fraunces', Georgia, serif;
    --sans:'Inter Tight','Helvetica Neue',sans-serif;
    --mono:'Geist Mono','SF Mono',monospace;
  }
  *,*::before,*::after{box-sizing:border-box;margin:0;padding:0}
  html{scroll-behavior:smooth;background:#0a0a0a}
  body{
    background:#0a0a0a;
    color:var(--ink-on-dark);
    font-family:var(--sans);
    font-weight:400;
    line-height:1.5;
    -webkit-font-smoothing:antialiased;
    overflow-x:hidden;
  }
  img,video{max-width:100%;display:block}
  button{font-family:inherit;cursor:pointer;background:none;border:none;color:inherit}

  /* ============ THEME SECTIONS ============ */
  .theme-dark{background:var(--bg-dark);color:var(--ink-on-dark)}
  .theme-light{background:var(--bg-light);color:var(--ink-on-light)}
  .theme-dark .accent{color:var(--gold-on-dark)}
  .theme-light .accent{color:var(--gold-on-light)}

  /* ============ NAV ============ */
  .nav{
    position:fixed;top:0;left:0;right:0;z-index:50;
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
    padding:18px 40px;
    background:rgba(10,10,10,0.85);
    backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
    -webkit-backdrop-filter:blur(20px);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-dark);
  }
  .nav-logo{
    font-family:var(--mono);
    font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.3em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-on-dark);
  }
  .nav-logo b{color:var(--gold-on-dark);font-weight:500}
  .nav-links{display:flex;gap:32px}
  .nav-links a{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.2em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark);
    text-decoration:none;transition:color .3s ease;
  }
  .nav-links a:hover{color:var(--ink-on-dark)}
  @media(max-width:768px){
    .nav{padding:14px 18px}
    .nav-links{display:none}
  }

  /* ============ HERO (DARK) ============ */
  .hero{
    position:relative;
    min-height:100vh;
    overflow:hidden;
    padding:120px 40px 80px;
    background:
      radial-gradient(ellipse at 70% 50%, rgba(232,201,138,0.06) 0%, transparent 55%),
      #0a0a0a;
  }
  .hero-grid{
    position:relative;z-index:3;
    width:100%;max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:1.05fr 1fr;
    gap:60px;align-items:center;
    min-height:calc(100vh - 200px);
  }
  @media(max-width:1000px){
    .hero-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}
    .hero{padding:110px 20px 60px}
  }
  .hero-tag{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.4em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold-on-dark);
    margin-bottom:32px;display:flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;
    animation:fadeUp 1s ease .2s both;
  }
  .hero-tag::before{content:"";width:40px;height:1px;background:var(--gold-on-dark)}
  .hero-title{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:300;
    font-size:clamp(56px, 9vw, 130px);line-height:0.92;letter-spacing:-0.03em;
    margin-bottom:36px;color:var(--ink-on-dark);
    animation:fadeUp 1s ease .4s both;
  }
  .hero-title i{font-style:italic;font-weight:300;color:var(--gold-on-dark)}
  .hero-sub{
    font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:300;
    font-size:clamp(15px, 1.2vw, 18px);line-height:1.7;
    max-width:500px;color:#d1ccc0;
    margin-bottom:48px;
    animation:fadeUp 1s ease .6s both;
  }
  .hero-meta{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr);gap:24px;
    padding-top:28px;border-top:1px solid var(--line-dark);
    animation:fadeUp 1s ease .8s both;max-width:500px;
  }
  .hero-meta div{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark)}
  .hero-meta div b{display:block;color:var(--ink-on-dark);font-weight:500;font-size:13px;margin-bottom:6px;letter-spacing:0.05em}
  .hero-visual{
    position:relative;aspect-ratio:4/5;
    background:url('images/collection-hero.jpeg') center/cover no-repeat;
    border:1px solid var(--line-dark);overflow:hidden;
  }
  .hero-visual::after{
    content:"";position:absolute;inset:0;
    background:linear-gradient(135deg, transparent 50%, rgba(10,10,10,0.5) 100%);
  }
  .hero-visual-tag{
    position:absolute;bottom:20px;left:20px;right:20px;z-index:2;
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.25em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:#fff;
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;
    padding-top:14px;border-top:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.4);
  }
  @media(max-width:1000px){.hero-visual{max-height:60vh}}
  @keyframes fadeUp{from{opacity:0;transform:translateY(30px)}to{opacity:1;transform:translateY(0)}}

  /* ============ EDITORIAL (LIGHT) ============ */
  .editorial{
    padding:140px 40px;
    background:var(--bg-light);
    border-top:1px solid var(--bg-dark);
    border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-light);
    color:var(--ink-on-light);
  }
  @media(max-width:900px){.editorial{padding:90px 20px}}
  .editorial-grid{
    max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:80px;align-items:start;
  }
  @media(max-width:900px){.editorial-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr;gap:40px}}
  .editorial-label{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.4em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold-on-light);
    margin-bottom:32px;
  }
  .editorial h2{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:300;
    font-size:clamp(38px, 4.5vw, 64px);line-height:1.05;letter-spacing:-0.02em;
    color:var(--ink-on-light);
  }
  .editorial h2 i{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-on-light);font-weight:400}
  .editorial-body p{
    font-size:16px;line-height:1.75;color:#3a3528;
    font-weight:300;margin-bottom:22px;
  }
  .editorial-body p:first-child::first-letter{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-size:64px;float:left;line-height:0.85;
    padding:6px 12px 0 0;color:var(--gold-on-light);font-weight:400;
  }
  .editorial-stats{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(3,1fr);gap:24px;
    margin-top:48px;padding-top:36px;border-top:1px solid var(--line-light);
  }
  .editorial-stats b{
    display:block;font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:300;
    font-size:38px;color:var(--ink-on-light);letter-spacing:-0.02em;margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .editorial-stats span{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--ink-dim-on-light);text-transform:uppercase}

  /* ============ COLLECTION (LIGHT) ============ */
  .collection{
    padding:120px 40px 80px;
    background:var(--bg-light);
    color:var(--ink-on-light);
  }
  @media(max-width:768px){.collection{padding:80px 18px 40px}}
  .collection-inner{max-width:1500px;margin:0 auto}
  .collection-head{
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;
    margin-bottom:70px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:24px;
  }
  .collection-head h2{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:300;
    font-size:clamp(40px,6vw,84px);line-height:0.95;letter-spacing:-0.025em;
    color:var(--ink-on-light);
  }
  .collection-head h2 i{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-on-light);font-weight:400}
  .collection-head-side{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--ink-dim-on-light);
    text-transform:uppercase;text-align:right;line-height:1.8;
  }
  .collection-head-side b{color:var(--ink-on-light);font-weight:500}

  /* Cards grid */
  .grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);
    gap:1px;background:var(--line-light);
    border:1px solid var(--line-light);
  }
  @media(max-width:1200px){.grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
  @media(max-width:640px){.grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}

  .card{
    background:var(--bg-dark);
    padding:24px 22px 26px;
    color:var(--ink-on-dark);
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;
    position:relative;overflow:hidden;
  }
  .card-num{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.3em;color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark);
    text-transform:uppercase;display:flex;justify-content:space-between;margin-bottom:18px;
  }
  .card-img{
    aspect-ratio:1/1;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;
    margin:0 auto 22px;width:100%;
    background:transparent;position:relative;
  }
  .card-img img{
    max-height:100%;max-width:100%;object-fit:contain;
    transition:opacity .4s ease, transform .6s ease;
  }
  .card-img img.alt{position:absolute;inset:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:contain;opacity:0}
  .card:hover .card-img img.main{opacity:0}
  .card:hover .card-img img.alt{opacity:1}
  .card-dots{display:flex;gap:6px;margin-bottom:12px}
  .card-dots span{width:9px;height:9px;border-radius:50%;border:1px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.15)}
  .card-name{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:400;font-size:24px;letter-spacing:-0.01em;
    color:var(--ink-on-dark);margin-bottom:4px;
  }
  .card-meta{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.2em;text-transform:uppercase;
    color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark);margin-bottom:20px;
  }
  .card-desc{
    font-size:12.5px;line-height:1.55;color:#bcb6a8;
    font-weight:300;margin-bottom:22px;
  }

  /* CONFIG inline */
  .config-label{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.3em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark);margin-bottom:10px;
  }
  .config-list{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:7px;margin-bottom:18px}
  .config-opt{
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;gap:10px;
    padding:11px 13px;width:100%;
    border:1px solid var(--line-dark);
    background:transparent;text-align:left;
    transition:all .25s ease;cursor:pointer;
  }
  .config-opt:hover:not([disabled]){border-color:rgba(232,201,138,0.4)}
  .config-opt.active{border-color:var(--gold-on-dark);background:rgba(232,201,138,0.06)}
  .config-opt[disabled]{opacity:0.35;cursor:not-allowed}
  .opt-info{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:2px}
  .opt-name{font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:500;font-size:12px;color:var(--ink-on-dark);letter-spacing:0.01em}
  .opt-sub{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:8.5px;letter-spacing:0.15em;color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark);text-transform:uppercase}
  .opt-price{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-size:16px;font-weight:300;
    color:var(--ink-on-dark);letter-spacing:-0.01em;white-space:nowrap;
  }

  .card-cta{
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
    padding:14px 18px;width:100%;
    background:var(--ink-on-dark);color:var(--bg-dark);
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10.5px;letter-spacing:0.22em;
    text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:500;
    text-decoration:none;text-align:center;
    transition:all .3s ease;border:1px solid var(--ink-on-dark);
  }
  .card-cta:hover{background:var(--gold-on-dark);border-color:var(--gold-on-dark);color:var(--bg-dark)}
  .card-cta-price{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.01em;text-transform:none}

  /* Otto Rosso special — same structure now (with real image) */

  /* ============ BRACELETS (LIGHT) ============ */
  .bracelets{
    padding:80px 40px 120px;
    background:var(--bg-light);
    color:var(--ink-on-light);
  }
  @media(max-width:768px){.bracelets{padding:60px 18px 80px}}
  .bracelets-inner{max-width:1500px;margin:0 auto}
  .bracelets-head{
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:flex-end;
    margin-bottom:36px;flex-wrap:wrap;gap:24px;
  }
  .bracelets-head h2{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:300;
    font-size:clamp(38px,5vw,60px);line-height:0.95;letter-spacing:-0.025em;
    color:var(--ink-on-light);
  }
  .bracelets-head h2 i{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-on-light);font-weight:400}
  .bracelets-head-side{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.2em;color:var(--ink-dim-on-light);
    text-transform:uppercase;text-align:right;line-height:1.8;
  }
  .bracelets-head-side b{color:var(--ink-on-light);font-weight:500}
  .bracelets-intro{
    font-size:15px;line-height:1.7;color:#3a3528;font-weight:300;
    max-width:680px;margin-bottom:50px;
  }
  .b-grid{
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(5,1fr);gap:1px;
    background:var(--line-light);border:1px solid var(--line-light);
  }
  @media(max-width:1100px){.b-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
  @media(max-width:560px){.b-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .b-card{
    background:var(--bg-dark);color:var(--ink-on-dark);
    padding:22px 20px;
    display:flex;flex-direction:column;
  }
  .b-img{
    aspect-ratio:1/1;background:var(--bg-dark-2);margin-bottom:18px;overflow:hidden;
  }
  .b-img img{width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;transition:transform .7s ease}
  .b-card:hover .b-img img{transform:scale(1.05)}
  .b-label{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.2em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark);margin-bottom:6px;
  }
  .b-name{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:400;font-size:18px;
    letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:var(--ink-on-dark);margin-bottom:14px;
  }
  .b-cta{
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
    padding:11px 14px;margin-top:auto;text-decoration:none;
    background:var(--ink-on-dark);color:var(--bg-dark);
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:9.5px;letter-spacing:0.2em;
    text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:500;
    transition:all .3s ease;border:1px solid var(--ink-on-dark);
  }
  .b-cta:hover{background:var(--gold-on-dark);border-color:var(--gold-on-dark)}
  .b-price{font-family:var(--serif);font-size:14px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:-0.01em;text-transform:none}

  /* ============ SERVICE (DARK) ============ */
  .service{
    background:var(--bg-dark-2);color:var(--ink-on-dark);
    border-top:1px solid var(--line-dark);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-dark);
    padding:80px 40px;
  }
  @media(max-width:768px){.service{padding:60px 18px}}
  .service-grid{
    max-width:1400px;margin:0 auto;
    display:grid;grid-template-columns:repeat(4,1fr);gap:1px;
    background:var(--line-dark);
  }
  @media(max-width:900px){.service-grid{grid-template-columns:repeat(2,1fr)}}
  @media(max-width:520px){.service-grid{grid-template-columns:1fr}}
  .service-item{background:var(--bg-dark-2);padding:30px 26px}
  .service-item .icn{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:300;font-size:36px;color:var(--gold-on-dark);
    margin-bottom:18px;letter-spacing:-0.03em;
  }
  .service-item h4{
    font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:500;font-size:13px;letter-spacing:0.1em;
    text-transform:uppercase;margin-bottom:10px;color:var(--ink-on-dark);
  }
  .service-item p{font-family:var(--sans);font-weight:300;font-size:13px;line-height:1.7;color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark)}

  /* ============ CONTACT (DARK) ============ */
  .contact{padding:140px 40px;text-align:center;background:var(--bg-dark);color:var(--ink-on-dark)}
  @media(max-width:768px){.contact{padding:80px 20px}}
  .contact-tag{
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:11px;letter-spacing:0.4em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--gold-on-dark);margin-bottom:28px;
  }
  .contact h2{
    font-family:var(--serif);font-weight:300;
    font-size:clamp(40px,6vw,84px);line-height:1;letter-spacing:-0.025em;
    margin-bottom:36px;color:var(--ink-on-dark);
  }
  .contact h2 i{font-style:italic;color:var(--gold-on-dark);font-weight:400}
  .contact p{font-size:16px;color:#c4bfb3;max-width:520px;margin:0 auto 48px;font-weight:300;line-height:1.7}
  .btn-wa{
    display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:14px;
    background:var(--ink-on-dark);color:var(--bg-dark);
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:12px;letter-spacing:0.2em;
    text-transform:uppercase;font-weight:500;
    padding:22px 40px;text-decoration:none;
    border:1px solid var(--ink-on-dark);transition:all .4s ease;
  }
  .btn-wa:hover{background:var(--gold-on-dark);border-color:var(--gold-on-dark);color:var(--bg-dark)}
  .btn-wa svg{width:18px;height:18px}

  /* ============ FOOTER ============ */
  footer{padding:60px 40px 40px;background:var(--bg-dark);border-top:1px solid var(--line-dark);text-align:center}
  footer p{font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.25em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark);line-height:2}
  footer p b{color:var(--gold-on-dark);font-weight:500}

  /* ============ FAB ============ */
  .fab{
    position:fixed;bottom:24px;right:24px;z-index:80;
    width:58px;height:58px;border-radius:50%;
    background:#25d366;color:white;
    display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;text-decoration:none;
    box-shadow:0 10px 36px rgba(37,211,102,0.4), 0 0 0 6px rgba(37,211,102,0.12);
    transition:transform .3s ease;
  }
  .fab:hover{transform:scale(1.08)}
  .fab svg{width:28px;height:28px}

  /* Section rule (dark divider) */
  .section-rule{
    background:var(--bg-dark);padding:0 40px;
    display:flex;justify-content:space-between;align-items:center;
    font-family:var(--mono);font-size:10px;letter-spacing:0.3em;
    text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--ink-dim-on-dark);
    height:60px;border-top:1px solid var(--line-dark);border-bottom:1px solid var(--line-dark);
  }
  .section-rule-inner{max-width:1500px;margin:0 auto;width:100%;display:flex;justify-content:space-between}
</style>
</head>
<body>

<!-- NAV -->
<nav class="nav">
  <div class="nav-logo">SWATCH <b>×</b> AUDEMARS PIGUET</div>
  <div class="nav-links">
    <a href="#collection">Collection</a>
    <a href="#bracelets">Bracelets</a>
    <a href="#editorial">L'Histoire</a>
    <a href="#contact">Contact</a>
  </div>
</nav>

<!-- HERO -->
<header class="hero">
  <div class="hero-grid">
    <div class="hero-text">
      <div class="hero-tag">Édition Limitée — 2026</div>
      <h1 class="hero-title">Royal <i>Pop</i></h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Huit pièces. Huit langues. Huit visions du chiffre 8.
        Une collaboration sans précédent entre Swatch et Audemars Piguet —
        l'art horloger de la Vallée de Joux rencontre l'audace Pop des années 80.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-meta">
        <div><b>Bioceramic</b>Matériau breveté Swatch</div>
        <div><b>Sistem51</b>Mouvement mécanique manuel</div>
        <div><b>90h+</b>Réserve de marche</div>
        <div><b>Swiss Made</b>Origine Suisse</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="hero-visual-tag">
        <span>Collection Royal Pop</span>
        <span>08 modèles</span>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</header>

<!-- EDITORIAL (LIGHT) -->
<section class="editorial" id="editorial">
  <div class="editorial-grid">
    <div>
      <div class="editorial-label">Chapitre 01 — La Rencontre</div>
      <h2>Deux maisons.<br>Un même <i>terrain</i><br>de jeu.</h2>
    </div>
    <div class="editorial-body">
      <p>Depuis 1875, Audemars Piguet écrit l'histoire de la haute horlogerie depuis Le Brassus. Swatch, depuis 1983, a redéfini la montre comme objet de culture pop. La rencontre des deux mondes donne naissance à la Royal Pop — une montre de poche en Bioceramic qui reprend les codes mythiques de la Royal Oak : lunette octogonale, huit vis hexagonales, motif Petite Tapisserie.</p>
      <p>Le mouvement Sistem51 manuel inédit — quinze brevets actifs, spiral Nivachron antimagnétique — anime chaque pièce avec plus de 90 heures de réserve de marche. Une prouesse mécanique habillée des couleurs vives du Pop Art.</p>
      <div class="editorial-stats">
        <div><b>08</b><span>Modèles uniques</span></div>
        <div><b>40<small style="font-size:18px">mm</small></b><span>Diamètre boîtier</span></div>
        <div><b>15</b><span>Brevets actifs</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

